                  </hi>. I keep a school in Camden-street, Islington. The prisoner was in my house on the 24th of April—she came to ask for a small</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183705080106"></xptr>
               <p>debt that was due to a laundress, and I refused to give it, not having seen her before—I had some cloaks hanging up, and missed one—this is it, it belongs to Mr. Philipe.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370508-name-731" type="witnessName">
